ZH: 我正在注视着小鸟在天空中飞翔。
EN: I am watching the little bird as it flies in the sky.

ZH: 这支笔是用红色墨水注射的。
EN: This pen is filled with red ink.

ZH: 请不要把太多的注解放在一本书的每一页上。
EN: Please don't put too many footnotes on every page of a book.

ZH: 他的评论中注入了一些幽默感。
EN: He injected some humor into his comments.

ZH: 这位画家注重细节。
EN: This painter pays attention to details.

ZH: 我需要在这篇文章的结尾处加一点注脚。
EN: I need to add a little footnote at the end of this article.

ZH: 他用标签注明了每个文件夹的内容。
EN: He labeled each folder to indicate its contents.

ZH: 她一看就知道这封信是由他亲自注写的。
EN: She could tell at a glance that the letter was personally handwritten by him.

ZH: 这次会议上，他给每个人发了一份有关议程的注释。
EN: During this meeting, he distributed notes to everyone regarding the agenda.

ZH: 请尽量在上交论文前注明你的名字和学号。
EN: Please try to annotate your name and student number before submitting the paper.

ZH: 这本书附有解释器对每个单词出现的注解。
EN: This book is accompanied by an interpreter's annotations for every word.

ZH: 在手术前，医生使用药物注射止痛。
EN: Before the surgery, the doctor administered pain relief through medication injections.

ZH: 这本字典提供大量有关单词来源的注解。
EN: This dictionary provides extensive annotations on the origins of words.

