EN: When I saw this painting in the gallery, I was drawn to the vitality the artist injected onto the canvas with their brushstrokes.

ZH: 我喜欢这所博物馆，因为他们在每件艺术品旁注上了详细的介绍。
EN: I love this museum because they provide detailed descriptions next to each artwork.

